<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home page</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Salsa&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
    
        body{
            display: block;
            background-color: aquamarine;
        }
        
        .navbar{
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            width:100%;
            height: 12vh;
            background-color: rgb(2, 57, 2);
            color:white;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            border: 1px solid black;
        }

        h1{
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
        }
        
        .logo{
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-left: 3%;
        }
        
        .middle{
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-left: 10px;
            margin-right: 2%;
        }
        
        .p1{
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            border: none;
            margin-left: 1%;
            background-color: rgb(2, 57, 2);
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: "Salsa", cursive;
        }

        .p1:hover{
            color:yellow;
            transition: 0.7s;
        }

        .text{
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial, sans-serif;
            width:800px;
            margin-left: 15%;
            margin-top: 1%;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid black;
        }
        .button-contain{
            display: flex;
            margin-left: 10%;
            margin-right: 10%;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .b3{
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-left: 6%;
    padding: 3px;
    width:40%;
    height: 8vh;
    background-color: crimson;
    border-radius: 20px;
    color:white;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-family: "Salsa", cursive;
}

.b3:hover{
    background-color: rgb(158, 13, 13);
    color:white;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    transition: 0.7s;
    opacity: 0.7;
}

        #b31{
            background-color:red;
        }
        #b32{
            background-color:green;
        }
        </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <span class="logo">SYNDERGAMES</span>
        <div class="middle">
            <button class="p1" onclick="redirectToHome()">Home</button>
            <button class="p1" onclick="redirectToAbout()">About</button>
            <button class="p1" onclick="redirectToGames()">Games</button>
            <button class="p1" onclick="redirectToAuthor()">Author</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <center><h1>Home</h1></center>
    <div class="text">
        Welcome to SYNDERGAMES! Here, we're excited to introduce you to an immersive gaming experience featuring three captivating games: Tic Tac Toe, Hangman, and Rock Paper Scissors. <br>
        <br><br>
        Each game has been meticulously crafted using JavaScript, providing an engaging and interactive environment for players of all ages.<br>
        <br><br>
        Each of these games showcases the versatility and power of JavaScript in game development.<br>
        From strategic thinking to linguistic prowess to quick reflexes, our games offer something for every player to enjoy and master.<br>
        So come, dive into the world of gaming excellence, and let JavaScript power your journey to victory!<br>
    </div>
    <div class="button-contain">
        <button class="b3" onclick="redirectToGames()" id="b31">Start Playing!</button>
        <button class="b3" onclick="redirectToAbout()" id="b32">Know More!</button>
    </div>
    <script>
        function redirectToHome() {
            window.location.href = "/home";
        }
        function redirectToAbout() {
            window.location.href = "/about";
        }
        function redirectToGames() {
            window.location.href = "/games";
        }
        function redirectToAuthor() {
            window.location.href = "/author";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>